            "12.1",
            "11.8",
            "11.5",
            "11.9"
        );
    }

    println!();
    println!("{}", "Note: APM data collection in progress. Showing placeholder values.".yellow().dimmed());
    println!("{}", "Database integration and historical backfill coming in issues #649-651.".yellow().dimmed());

